data.description: Motivated Seller:  Updated, Renovated Brick Home situated on a Large Corner Lot in the Heart of Madisonville is Zoned for Residential or Retail/Office Commercial Use (SF2 per City).  This beautiful Brick Home features 3 Bedrooms, 2 full Bathrooms, has so many improvements; beautiful laminate (waterproof) flooring, farmhouse contemporary kitchen with quartz countertops, new appliances, pantry, open concept kitchen/living room, fireplace, formal dining room/bonus room and lots of natural light throughout.  Outdoors, there is a 2-car detached carport on the large .596 Acre Lot that displays several mature trees, and a fence.  Currently used as a full-time residence, make this your new home or retail location.  Offering a convenient location to all city amenities, there is quick access to Hwy 21, and I-45; approximately 45 minutes to Bryan College Station and 30 minutes to Huntsville.
